小堇","from":494.97,"location":2,"to":496.64},{"content":"这样我就感觉能把饭团烤好了","from":496.64,"location":2,"to":500.43},{"content":"真是学到了呢！","from":501.39,"location":2,"to":502.85},{"content":"不过啊","from":502.85,"location":2,"to":504.19},{"content":"我就算没有那些小诀窍","from":504.19,"location":2,"to":505.73},{"content":"也绝对不会烤失败的！","from":505.73,"location":2,"to":508.57},{"content":"好厉害","from":508.57,"location":2,"to":509.57},{"content":"你是怎么做到的啊 姐姐？","from":509.57,"location":2,"to":511.94},{"content":"问得好","from":511.94,"location":2,"to":512.86},{"content":"那我就破例悄悄地告诉你们两个吧","from":512.86,"location":2,"to":515.41},{"content":"用微波炉热一下！","from":516.32,"location":2,"to":517.99},{"content":"原来如此！","from":517.99,"location":2,"to":519.58},{"content":"(舞伎家的料理人)","from":519.95,"location":2,"to":524.96},{"content":"(第 17 话 花街的圣诞节)","from":536.97,"location":2,"to":538.26},{"content":"圣诞节到了呢…\n(第 17 话 花街的圣诞节)","from":538.26,"location":2,"to":540.56},{"content":"(第 17 话 花街的圣诞节)","from":540.56,"location":2,"to":540.97},{"content":"圣诞节啊…\n(第 17 话 花街的圣诞节)","from":540.97,"location":2,"to":543.18},{"content":"在花街 并不会为圣诞节举办特别活动","from":543.68,"location":2,"to":547.9},{"content":"街上不会用彩灯来装饰","from":548.44,"location":2,"to":551.73},{"content":"也不会立起圣诞树","from":552.03,"location":2,"to":554.82},{"content":"要说能感受到的圣诞节氛围…","from":555.4,"location":2,"to":558.16},{"content":"晚上好","from":559.03,"location":2,"to":560.24},{"content":"您好您好！","from":561.04,"location":2,"to":562.29},{"content":"欢迎回来","from":562.29,"location":2,"to":563.7},{"content":"好久不见啊","from":564.21,"location":2,"to":566.54},{"content":"也就是茶舍老板娘的腰带绳扣\n(圣诞快乐)","from":567.21,"location":2,"to":570.13},{"content":"来来 这边请…","from":572.17,"location":2,"to":574.34},{"content":"或者花瓶里的鲜花\n(圣诞快乐)","from":574.92,"location":2,"to":577.05},{"content":"妈妈","from":579.51,"location":2,"to":580.35},{"content":"这个分给大家吧","from":580.35,"location":2,"to":581.51},{"content":"还有客人们当成礼物送来的蛋糕\n(圣诞快乐)","from":581.97,"location":2,"to":584.85},{"content":"蛋糕","from":587.14,"location":2,"to":588.35},{"content":"蛋糕啊","from":588.35,"location":2,"to":589.86},{"content":"蛋糕是吧","from":589.86,"location":2,"to":591.69},{"content":"你们说的礼物蛋糕是什么？","from":593.65,"location":2,"to":597.07},{"content":"就是客人带来的圣诞蛋糕","from":597.36,"location":2,"to":601.62},{"content":"昨天为止我都吃了5个呢","from":602.03,"location":2,"to":604.79},{"content":"我吃了4个 我输了","from":605.54,"location":2,"to":607.83},{"content":"我也吃了4个","from":607.83,"location":2,"to":609.29},{"content":"虽然有点撑","from":609.29,"location":2,"to":610.29},{"content":"但是难得人家送来的嘛","from":610.29,"location":2,"to":612.63},{"content":"是啊是啊","from":612.63,"location":2,"to":613.5},{"content":"必须心怀感激地全部吃掉才行啊","from":613.5,"location":2,"to":616.05},{"content":"好撑啊","from":616.22,"location":2,"to":618.09},{"content":"请…请等一下…","from":619.26,"location":2,"to":621.51},{"content":"我可是连1个都还没吃到呢…蛋糕","from":622.01,"location":2,"to":627.27},{"content":"我暂时都不想看到鲜奶油和草莓了","from":627.64,"location":2,"to":632.11},{"content":"我也是","from":632.11,"location":2,"to":633.52},{"content":"真是的","from":633.52,"location":2,"to":634.53},{"content":"暂时不想再看到圣诞蛋糕了呢","from":634.53,"location":2,"to":637.65},{"content":"是吗","from":643.37,"location":2,"to":644.58},{"content":"怪不得前阵子我准备做蛋糕的时候 妈妈她…","from":644.58,"location":2,"to":648.12},{"content":"受够鲜奶油和草莓了","from":648.12,"location":2,"to":651.96},{"content":"这么说来着","from":651.96,"location":2,"to":653.38},{"content":"就连妈妈也…","from":654.3,"location":2,"to":656.13},{"content":"鲜奶油…草莓…","from":657.38,"location":2,"to":659.55},{"content":"只有我一个人没过圣诞节…","from":660.18,"location":2,"to":662.8},{"content":"真是的","from":669.69,"location":2,"to":670.48},{"content":"小题大做了啦 小堇","from":670.48,"location":2,"to":672.48},{"content":"可是…圣诞节…","from":672.48,"location":2,"to":675.23},{"content":"因为有的材料已经用掉了","from":678.61,"location":2,"to":680.45},{"content":"蛋糕是没法烤了…\n( 味道浓厚 风味十足 需冷藏  鲜奶油)","from":680.45,"location":2,"to":682.24},{"content":"但还有剩下的材料哦","from":685.58,"location":2,"to":687.37},{"content":"有作为点心的水果